(=== BOOK SUMMARY ===) Tj T*
(The Springer Handbook of Robotics is the most comprehensive reference work in the) Tj T*
(field of robotics. Comprising over 2200 pages and dozens of chapters, it covers the) Tj T*
(absolute state-of-the-art in robotics foundations, design, sensing, control, mobile) Tj T*
(robots, field robotics, humanoid robots, and ethical/social implications.) Tj T*
